The paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques for learning entity and concept representations from large scale knowledge bases. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves deep learning techniques and neural networks, which are commonly associated with cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which are associated with cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves knowledge bases, which are associated with cs.DB (Databases).
